      "_desc": "Comparison-table style module with 3 p_image* variables bound to src on .esd-gen-image* classes (static tick markers that should NOT be LLM-populated), plus a nesting hazard where p_description's outer <p>.esd-gen-description wraps an inner <strong>.esd-gen-p-row_title_1 binding. Inspector should flag both patterns + suggest the HTML-comment contract.",
      "id": 9002,
      "uid": "pqr-uid-9002",
